All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
Command
The Command interface defines the structure for commands that operate on a database table.
DeleteCommand
The DeleteCommand class handles deleting a record from a database table.
InsertCommand
The InsertCommand class handles inserting a record into a database table.
Main
The Main class demonstrates the usage of the Command pattern for performing database table operations with transactional support.
Table
The Table class represents a simple database table that can store, delete, and update records.
TransactionManager
The TransactionManager class handles the execution of a sequence of commands as a transaction.
UpdateCommand
The UpdateCommand class handles updating a record in a database table.
